The elven kingdom located on the highway between Darkwind City and the
frozen tundra is the home of the Silver Elves. Silver Elves are also
known as Moon Elves. Silver Elf culture tends towards goodness and
lawfulness so as to please Luna, the moon Goddess. Silver Elves have
keen night vision, exude charisma, and are typically more intelligent, 
though less wise, than other races. Physically they are more nimble 
than what is typical, though they are rather fragile of constitution.
